⚠️ IMPORTANT NOTES (read this)
1. You still need to copy wallpapers

Your script expects this directory populated:

~/Pictures/wallpaper/


👉 Easiest way:

cp -r your_backup/wallpaper ~/Pictures/

2. You still need zsh-powerlevel10k and pokemon-colorscripts


3. Monitor names may differ

You hardcoded:

DP-1
HDMI-A-1


If it breaks:

hyprctl monitors


Then update wallpp.
